    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A WW2 Tower Defense game, with minor aspects of an RTS game. Build up an army to defend your base. Progress throughout the game to get stronger units and strategically change your loadout for each map to get the upper edge on the enemy forces. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 30 meticulously designed units representing both Allies and Axis forces </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Command a diverse mix of tanks and infantry, ensuring a rich and dynamic battlefield experience </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Embark on dynamic campaigns where you orchestrate the combined might of American and British forces or spearhead the Axis dominance by uniting Germany and Italy </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Expansive selection of playable maps across various theaters of war </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Four difficulty levels to cater to a wide range of player skills and preferences </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Tailor your gameplay with customizable unit selection for a personalized experience </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Accelerate the pace of gameplay with a versatile fast-forward feature, offering 1x, 2x, and 3x speed options </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless waves of procedural gameplay for an infinite challenge </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Tactical flexibility as most units are mobile, allowing strategic repositioning </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Enhance your tactical advantage by assembling units into trios, enabling them to engage in battle together and unleash their combined strength. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Command with precision as your units exhibit advanced pathfinding, skillfully shooting on the move to maintain a relentless offensive</p></li></ul>",
